    <title>Pandas筆記</title>
    <url>/2020/05/21/Pandas/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="Pandas"><a href="#Pandas" class="headerlink" title="Pandas"></a>Pandas</h1><p>pandas document<br><a href="https://pandas.pydata.org/docs/pandas.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://pandas.pydata.org/docs/pandas.pdf</a><br><a href="https://pandas.pydata.org/pandas-docs/stable/reference/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://pandas.pydata.org/pandas-docs/stable/reference/index.html</a><br>資料科學家的 pandas 實戰手冊：掌握 40 個實用數據技巧<br><a href="https://leemeng.tw/practical-pandas-tutorial-for-aspiring-data-scientists.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://leemeng.tw/practical-pandas-tutorial-for-aspiring-data-scientists.html</a></p>
<h2 id="安裝pandas"><a href="#安裝pandas" class="headerlink" title="安裝pandas"></a>安裝pandas</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip install pandas</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="新建DataFrame-document"><a href="#新建DataFrame-document" class="headerlink" title="新建DataFrame(document)"></a>新建DataFrame(<a href="https://pandas.pydata.org/pandas-docs/stable/reference/api/pandas.DataFrame.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">document</a>)</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">import pandas as pd</span><br><span class="line">dic &#x3D; &#123;&#39;weekday&#39;: [&#39;Sun&#39;, &#39;Sun&#39;, &#39;Mon&#39;, &#39;Mon&#39;],</span><br><span class="line">        &#39;city&#39;: [&#39;Austin&#39;, &#39;Dallas&#39;, &#39;Austin&#39;, &#39;Dallas&#39;],</span><br><span class="line">        &#39;visitor&#39;: [139, 237, 326, 456]&#125;</span><br><span class="line">visitor1 &#x3D; pd.DataFrame(dic)</span><br><span class="line">print(visitor1)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="讀取CSV-excel-檔案"><a href="#讀取CSV-excel-檔案" class="headerlink" title="讀取CSV(excel)檔案"></a>讀取CSV(excel)檔案</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">import pandas as pd</span><br><span class="line">app_train &#x3D; pd.read_csv(&#39;application_train.csv&#39;)</span><br><span class="line">print(app_train)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>其他類型讀取可看<br><a href="https://pandas.pydata.org/pandas-docs/stable/reference/io.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://pandas.pydata.org/pandas-docs/stable/reference/io.html</a></p>
<h2 id="如何知道資料的-row-數以及-column-數"><a href="#如何知道資料的-row-數以及-column-數" class="headerlink" title="如何知道資料的 row 數以及 column 數"></a>如何知道資料的 row 數以及 column 數</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 如何知道資料的 row 數以及 column 數</span><br><span class="line"># (row-count, column-count)</span><br><span class="line">app_train.shape</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="有什麼欄位"><a href="#有什麼欄位" class="headerlink" title="有什麼欄位"></a>有什麼欄位</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 有什麼欄位, show出欄位名稱</span><br><span class="line">(r, c) &#x3D; app_train.axes</span><br><span class="line">print(c)</span><br><span class="line"># or</span><br><span class="line">print(app_train.columns)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="索引"><a href="#索引" class="headerlink" title="索引"></a>索引</h2><p>.ix[::, ::] 可以（利用索引值或欄位）選擇 data frame 區段（axis=0)横向，(axis=1)列向<br>ps. 現已不推薦使用<br>.loc[label] 這是嚴格基於標籤的索引<br>.iloc[inte] 這是嚴格基於整數位置的索引</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">app_train.loc[10:20,&#39;SK_ID_CURR&#39;:&#39;NAME_CONTRACT_TYPE&#39;]</span><br><span class="line"># or</span><br><span class="line">app_train.iloc[10:20,0:3]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="One-Hot-Encoder-document"><a href="#One-Hot-Encoder-document" class="headerlink" title="One Hot Encoder : (document)"></a>One Hot Encoder : (<a href="https://pandas.pydata.org/pandas-docs/stable/reference/api/pandas.get_dummies.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">document</a>)</h2><p>轉換字串/類別類型的資料到數值的資料類型</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pd.get_dummies(df)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>可針對想要執行的column做指定</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pd.get_dummies(df.ColumnName)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
